WEBVTT

00:44.617 --> 00:46.252
All clear.

00:46.686 --> 00:49.393
Mount pickets and keep a watch.

00:49.427 --> 00:53.267
Bring hemp, wrap the officers.

00:53.301 --> 00:55.139
Bury the rest...

00:55.173 --> 00:57.479
over there.

01:19.591 --> 01:22.331
That as Thou hast raised up
my body from fast and sound sleep,

01:22.365 --> 01:25.904
so also Thou would deliver
my mind from the sleep of sin.

01:28.173 --> 01:31.045
Did they change the prayers
for middle sleep?

01:32.384 --> 01:35.220
I'm praying for us.

01:35.254 --> 01:38.994
Before first sleep, second sleep,
morning, afternoon, and night again.

01:46.339 --> 01:48.542
Don't you see
that this plague is a sign?

01:48.577 --> 01:51.080
- Mary...
- God is sending you a message.

01:51.115 --> 01:53.451
Look, it's not a plague.

01:53.485 --> 01:55.789
It's maggots. They happen.

01:58.864 --> 02:02.268
Perhaps it's the Lord's grace.

02:02.302 --> 02:04.872
We can leave here and move in
with your father at Whitehall

02:04.906 --> 02:06.710
before winter comes.

02:11.653 --> 02:14.492
Come here. Come here.

02:14.526 --> 02:16.796
Look.

02:18.833 --> 02:20.202
You see that?

02:20.236 --> 02:23.040
We still have over half our crop

02:23.074 --> 02:25.413
stored safe in the shed.

02:25.448 --> 02:28.050
I'll haul it to the green
tomorrow and sell it.

02:29.553 --> 02:32.088
How much will that make?

02:32.123 --> 02:35.294
It'll be enough to make it
through the winter.

02:35.329 --> 02:38.296
Then what about spring? We'll have
nothing left to reseed the field.

02:38.331 --> 02:40.399
We're not moving in with my father.

02:56.809 --> 02:58.906
Did we wake you up, little man?

02:58.941 --> 03:01.675
Come here, come here.

03:01.709 --> 03:04.943
Shh, shh, shh, shh, shh.

03:04.977 --> 03:06.707
Here, I'll show you something.

03:09.279 --> 03:12.432
What's in here? Huh?

03:14.149 --> 03:15.746
Oh.

03:17.881 --> 03:19.915
What's this?

03:21.115 --> 03:23.048
Ooh.

03:23.082 --> 03:24.782
Pirate treasure.

03:24.816 --> 03:26.950
Pirate treasure.

03:26.984 --> 03:30.435
Yeah, your pa's made arrangements.

03:31.653 --> 03:34.155
Our little secret,
though, eh, Sprout?

03:52.406 --> 03:54.604
Abraham!

04:02.077 --> 04:04.475
Luke! Jeremiah!

04:04.509 --> 04:06.077
Oh, mercy!

04:08.047 --> 04:09.281
Get back inside!

